<TITLE> bdnews24.com to be online media partner for BASIS Software Expo 2009 </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Nov 24 (bdnews24.com) bdnews24.com will be the official online media partner of 'BASIS Soft Expo 2009', to be held next January. A Tawhid of BASIS and Rashed Ahsan for bdnews24.com signed a media agreement on Monday at BASIS's Karwan Bazar office. Bangladesh Association of Software and Information Service also signed similar agreements with ATN Bangla as television media partner, English-language daily New Age as newspaper partner, Radio Today as radio partner and Link Three Technology as the official ISP. Chief adviser of ATN Bangla Saiful Bari, managing editor of New Age Ershad Khandokar, Syed Saif of Radio Today and chairman of Link Three Technology Sheikh Raihan Ahmed signed the agreements for their media organisations
